</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-110_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0c8ae6e9-592f-4dd9-a0d8-0ae6dcc15bfc"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">By identifying trends and cross-referencing training data with KPIs, organisations can make smarter decisions about workforce development, risk mitigation, and quality assurance.
